I also learn how to apply text to the sketch with the text placed at (10,100) When thinking about the x and y coordinates of the sketch I imagined an upside down grid. Where the x values run along the top side and the y values run along the left side. Using the same sketch I changed a few values of the image and replaced them with a cam.image instead. I then went on to change the “n” int to see what effects were produced.

I may look into ways I can replace the mouse movement with another input method, maybe for the brightest pixel or a colour that I could track. I know using a Kinect and tracking is possible but Ill have to see if I can learn this before the deadline.

